{"tid":1280793,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"驚畀人上門拉既入一入來，心理輔導一下大家","createTime":"2019-07-03T05:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:39:53.000Z","uid":43751,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c36fb36dafa71493f4dcd5abcc6a011b20c56e31","tid":1280793,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"冷靜一啲睇個問題<br />\n唔好係政治角度諗<br />\n好多野都只係白色恐怖<br />\n因為未知 所以擔心<br />\n問下自己<br />\n<br />\n1.有冇可能觸犯法例<br />\n2.如果觸犯法例，可能係觸犯邊幾條<br />\n3.如果觸犯左，最壞打算會有乜刑罰<br />\n4.會唔會有人上門拉<br />\n5.即而上門拉你，會唔會係第一班人拉你<br />\n6.夠唔夠証據入你<br />\n<br />\n起碼預算左最壞結果先<br />\n唔係世界未日<br />\n唔好驚到自殺<br />\n<br />\n好多網傳網傳網傳<br />\n搵哂啲Fact checked 既新聞<br />\n分析下自己咩情況先"},{"pid":"0dfe10c363ac49a82e63fa7df8421a72d14b36c7","tid":1280793,"uid":43751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"理性<br />\n大部分人既心理問題係過度思考<br />\n未發生既事，無可能發生既事<br />\n杞人憂天<br />\n<br />\n就正如有學生因為一兩次考試而自殺<br />\n其實大家都知係好無價值<br />\n只不過係情緒病 令腦分泌不正常<br />\n<br />\n好似張國榮 Linkin park 主音<br />\n有才華 金錢 愛情<br />\n都係因為情緒問題而了結<br />\n<br />\n冷靜啲睇<br />\n最壞要坐幾多年<br />\n李家超嗰日都講埋 入立法會嗰班最高可以判兩年<br />\n值唔值得為左人生兩年 而放棄條命"},{"pid":"d736381200200ae80c08ffffd417c1ad0f7058d1","tid":1280793,"uid":3273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"小明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb5f5875d0d358bfaab3086f7ba18f2aea545c8","tid":1280793,"uid":237712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"小明分享多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ec72128c7c658db2eeb2d745f8bd000880b7ca","tid":1280793,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"大家一定要確立左自己有情緒病先有得醫<br />\n情緒病 會令你不能理性<br />\n好似啲小學生被老師鬧兩句就跳樓<br />\n其實佢地都知道 自己係唔值得<br />\n奈何人腦 本身就以感情主導理智<br />\n尤其腦分泌失平衡<br />\n<br />\n正如係街 同阿伯嘈兩句<br />\n一拳打死左個阿伯<br />\n就係&ldquo;衝動&rdquo;控制左理智"},{"pid":"c7f348862e15e84ab6eedaeb46a0b1410979ebb5","tid":1280793,"uid":43751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:13:24.000Z","msg":"落街食個m 記<br />\n再去公園散步兩個鐘<br />\n離開間房 吸下啲新鮮空氣先"},{"pid":"5bf55668910e3edccab21d7e44f043398fb635c1","tid":1280793,"uid":15557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"小明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0e0907ddb6acd9112242588d3e9cc237f58930","tid":1280793,"uid":17726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"我記得明仔好似係928過來人？俾狗咬佢d post，依家都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：有買書同追開故"},{"pid":"3b7171a942a6d5f08556081dfc52614f15eee1f5","tid":1280793,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:04:05.000Z","msg":"小明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d79d6bbd38dd9b61d7ddab079134d2fbec768b3","tid":1280793,"uid":144014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"小ming<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">小m</span>"}]}